channel.title: Submitting Your Work and Bonus Missions :: Java Web Development
channel.description: Sanity Check At this point, all autograding tests should be passing. To be sure, right-click on the org.launchcode.techjobs.mvc package in src/test/java and select Run tests in… If any test fails, evaluate the failure/error message and go back to fix your code. You might also want to check your app’s behavior against that of our demo app . How to Submit To turn in your assignment and get credit, follow the submission instructions .
